0.0.9 refines mkcrossbuildenv script and adds BUILD
0.0.10-12 provide bugfixes and refinements
0.0.13 clarifies ARCH arm64 vs aarch64 in validate_target() fns
0.0.14 fixes permissions on files populating /etc/${PN}/files/
